{"id": 2078, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪种程度的职场监督会让你感到不舒服？", "description": "以前连办公室都是各有各的，现如今老板甚至可以通过工牌或办公椅监视员工了，在你看来，职场隐私的底线在哪里？（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2807, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171220184602afiR2X6svJIrd4bE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 256512, "content": "上班迟到要发红包，下班迟了周末加班什么都没。看得到的工作才是工作，看不到的就是偷懒。专业上半桶水，却非要来指挥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222648}, {"id": 256768, "content": "通过微信步数推测请假是干了什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547895}, {"id": 256531, "content": "监控微信。直接查看公司员工的微信聊天记录。我真是不知道是不是该去起诉公司老板", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711981}, {"id": 257310, "content": "到处都是摄像头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225662}, {"id": 256543, "content": "绩效考核", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983960}, {"id": 256811, "content": "办公室监控，不能忍，拿手机发条微信就会回头主任就现在身后", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776059}, {"id": 256812, "content": "临时布置两天完成一周的工作量", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223569}, {"id": 256834, "content": "上下班打卡 迟到一分钟就一块钱 忘打卡也扣钱。但是提前上班 或者加班几个小时都没有任何回报", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223620}, {"id": 257112, "content": "发工作手机，美其名曰福利，实际就是个带锁的定位器", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546141}, {"id": 258138, "content": "全方位无死角带录音的监控", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208661}, {"id": 256352, "content": "在我工作的时候盯着我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002171}, {"id": 256353, "content": "网络监控，知道自己电脑被监视却不能知道谁到底能获取哪些层次我们的信息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 377, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797764}, {"id": 256354, "content": "共享实时位置查岗", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720773}, {"id": 256355, "content": "每周汇报工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 256611, "content": "电饭锅很纠结", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335558}, {"id": 256357, "content": "在和我说话的时候，不看我，一直盯着我的电脑屏幕。\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283795}, {"id": 256358, "content": "公司限制网络，视频、音乐的网站和软件都不能使用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870381}, {"id": 256359, "content": "老板转一圈又一圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211908}, {"id": 256360, "content": "用QQ联系工作被领导说上班聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55397}, {"id": 256362, "content": "查询材料价格等于逛淘宝！", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198151}, {"id": 256363, "content": "为什么没人催你下班？", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640021}, {"id": 256365, "content": "直接下发通告，任何人都可以通过邮箱直接举报，你最后都不知道怎么死的", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213941}, {"id": 256366, "content": "进度监控，明明说了大概一周完成，但老板每天都会问进度怎么样了？？催命一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879838}, {"id": 256367, "content": "事无巨细要报备！", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869548}, {"id": 256369, "content": "办公地24小时监控", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128553}, {"id": 256625, "content": "1.网络监控，\n2.工作既要求量也要求质。“极致”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219075}, {"id": 256371, "content": "科室无死角监控，并且领导把监控画面开着当办公电脑背景，意思就是，领导无论在桌面上做什么余光都是能看到我们在做什么的。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561493}, {"id": 256886, "content": "不同领导同时安排任务", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159207}, {"id": 256379, "content": "放假的时候任然会有人来找你…", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219249}, {"id": 256635, "content": "在密闭场合碰到熟人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222965}, {"id": 259196, "content": "考试时老师站在我面前", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911543}, {"id": 256642, "content": "上班时忙的昏天黑地，好容易熬到下班，却突然得到要加班迎接检查?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027558}, {"id": 256387, "content": "老板上班偷偷摸摸的来看你在搞啥子，", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222046}, {"id": 256388, "content": "限制使用几支杯子", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217198}, {"id": 256389, "content": "上班不能迟到，却常常加班，而且周末总突然打电话叫去加班。平时工作没有空闲的时间，办公室离领导非常近…", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187173}, {"id": 256390, "content": "来自资本家的一波压榨，有意见敢闹嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222069}, {"id": 256391, "content": "上下班考勤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 256393, "content": "你加要微信，朋友圈不能屏蔽，要注意你的动态", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222085}, {"id": 256399, "content": "被监视。这样压力太大了，无法全心工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050355}, {"id": 256404, "content": "不喜欢老板在后面订着看", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222164}, {"id": 256405, "content": "正装黑鞋工牌桌上不许放办公用品之外的东西不许在工位吃东西看！到！就！罚！钱！公司要正规化确迟迟不上保险", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222166}, {"id": 256406, "content": "强制员工安装定位app", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902112}, {"id": 256408, "content": "很好奇为什么各位在这种环境下还要坚持下去？难道是工资特高?", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979858}, {"id": 255385, "content": "老板总是不经意地来看我的电脑屏幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 229, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 256409, "content": "上一秒的工作任务，下一秒就夺命追问进展，感觉员工一旦离开视线就在度假模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949358}, {"id": 258713, "content": "小小声发句牢骚，立马大声追问，你不回复，马上紧追“你什么意思，说说呗，你说什么呢”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234886}, {"id": 255386, "content": "上班打卡开工，下班却不会停止接收工作消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 706, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 256410, "content": "打卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222204}, {"id": 256412, "content": "随时掌握我的全部时间的动态和工作进度，吃饭时间都能让我边吃边做报告?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211487}, {"id": 256415, "content": "投资人怕我忽悠你们钱就TM别找我来做CEO!", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198382}]}